description:
**Contributor Of**
* Perform activities in compliance with Discipline Development Plan of his/her PG/PL;
* Review Internal requirements, Customer Requirements, Specifications;
* In charge of the robust design / validation in line with the economical targets;
* Support technical architecture and standards assignments;
* Follow Standardization rules;
* Support design reviews, internal and with suppliers.


****His/her scope could include: all or part of the design, integration, validation of blocks / product****
**Complying With Disciplines Processes And Design Rules**
* Support Discipline design simulations/coding/validation;
* Support Discipline design calculations including worst case/statistical and support thermal studies;
* Support Disciplines tests.


****Management follow\\-up****
* Reports the progress of his/her tasks;
* Escalate risks
